            <h2 className="font-['Bebas_Neue'] text-4xl tracking-wider">NO ORDERS YET</h2>
            <p className="mt-2 font-bold text-gray-500 uppercase tracking-wide">Time to start your Serious Fried Chicken adventure!</p>
            <a 
